      <title>NYCB 的“巨额”CRE 风险敞口促使晨星 DBRS 降级</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/nycbs-outsized-cre-exposure-prompts-morningstar-dbrs-downgrade-2024-02-08/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周四，晨星 DBRS 将纽约社区银行的信用评级从“BBB（高）”下调至“BBB”，理由是与同行相比，该银行在商业房地产贷款方面的风险敞口“过大”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/nycbs-outsized-cre-exposure-prompts-morningstar-dbrs-downgrade-2024-02-08/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 14:12:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
